Text.string: Got a Vault Thief over here!
I spy with my little eye...
Hahaha, look at your busted-ass face!
Oh hell yes, look at that scrap!
Give this old man the chop!
Hey old man! Take on ME!
Hey Blondie! Lookin' real good! I mean it! What products you usin'?
Cool, a spy! Time to die!
Stay away from my junk, witch!
Mmm. I like my ladies... strong!
Your scalp's my ticket to the Great Vault!
You're out of your league, babycakes!
I'll get to you in a minute!
Present for you! You've earned it!
How about some friggin' DIVINE RETRIBUTION?!
Suck on this, you bloated crapstain!
Stand still so I can hit ya!
I got a gooood feeling about this!
Got some junk for you right here!
Ha! I scared off the bot! I think!
But I wanted to scrap that bot!
Had to be a friggin' Siren...
It's what I always hoped it'd be.
I ain't bait! Leave me alone!
Little in the middle but we got much rakks!
Get outta here, you flying pests!
Stomp on them! Stomp da whole world!
Got my work cut out for me...
Two for the price of one!
Cut 'em both in half! Four quarters!
What am I, seeing things now?!
I gotta reverse engineer that thing!
Maybe I could build one too!
Get that crap off my battlefield!
To the great junkyard at last!
I'll put your skeleton to good use, promise!
You're just another scrap heap now!
You should see your STUPID face right now!
I guess you're junk what I needed!
Gonna get ALL up in dat junk!
Hot damn, I love me some junk!
How do you like me now?
From scrap it came, to scrap it returns!
This is why we can't have nice things!
Oh, for the love o' junk!
What'd we ever do to you?! Oh, right. The killing.
So many things I never built...
Rage against the dying of the light...
You think... you're better than me?
A noble spirit embiggens the smallest me...
I liked Troy better. There, I said it!
I get it now. We're all just junk...
Remember me... like, a foot taller...
I repent! And I win... [death rattle]
Scrap to scrap... junk to junk...
I'm gonna make you into PUDDING!
This is one tough broad right here, yessiree!
Ridin' high on my favorite Tank!
Oh boy, oh boy, oh boy, we GOT 'em!
Got you! Got you! NOW DIE!
That'll teach you to mess with the family!
Let's get some more fighters out here!
Need more fam on the field!
We're running low, get me some backup!
Callin' on the fam for backup!
All right then, got some reinforcements!
Got you outnumbered, ya piss bucket!
Knocked me right on my ass!
Gonna force feed you my scrap!
I'm gonna knock you on your ass!
I'm gonna junk up your soul!
Ohhh, the rakks are gonna feed tonight!
Shoutout to my murder patron Tyreen!
Noo! No, no! I can't believe you DID THAT!
No, she can't be... you... you flippin' BASTARD!
Why'd you have to go and do that?! I'LL KILL YOU!
Nooo! No, no, no no no! RAGGHHH!
Nooo! Not my Tank! She was too young!
I'm so, so freakin' angry I'm losing it!
No, oh no! I'm gonna kill EVERYBODY!
Rrrrragh! I'm gonna GET THEM FOR THIS!
